    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="P91-52">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To learn the transport by the pain,</l>
                    <l>As blind men learn the sun;</l>
                    <l>To die of thirst, suspecting</l>
                    <l>That brooks in meadows run;</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>To stay the homesick, homesick feet</l>
                    <l>Upon a foreign shore</l>
                    <l>Haunted by native lands, the while,</l>
                    <l>And blue, beloved air </l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>This is the sovereign anguish,</l>
                    <l>This, the signal woe!</l>
                    <l>These are the patient laureates</l>
                    <l>Whose voices, trained below,</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Ascend in ceaseless carol,</l>
                    <l>Inaudible, indeed,</l>
                    <l>To us, the duller scholars</l>
                    <l>Of the mysterious bard!</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
        </body>
